column4: Woven by hand using select quality materials and traditional methods, the complex weave of each Willow Basket tells the story of the time and meticulous effort spent to craft each piece. Weaving is a centuries-old trade that was driven during the Industrial Revolution to fill the increased demand for functional containers. Willows are strong and flexible and the natural kink in each stem gives tightness and resilience to the finished basket. The generous sizes and assortment in shapes of our Willow Baskets enable them to be mainstay storage solutions in the home and garden with a quality that will allow them to become heirloom pieces for generations to come. Bring indoors during rain and frost to preserve longevity.

Woven by hand using select quality materials and traditional methods, the complex weave of each Willow Basket tells the story of the time and meticulous effort spent to craft each piece. Weaving is a centuries-old trade that was driven during the Industrial Revolution to fill the increased demand for functional containers. Willows are strong and flexible and the natural kink in each stem gives tightness and resilience to the finished basket. The generous sizes and assortment in shapes of our Willow Baskets enable them to be mainstay storage solutions in the home and garden with a quality that will allow them to become heirloom pieces for generations to come. Bring indoors during rain and frost to preserve longevity.

column4: Woven by hand using select quality materials and traditional methods, the complex weave of each Willow Basket tells the story of the time and meticulous effort spent to craft each piece. Weaving is a centuries-old trade that was driven during the Industrial Revolution to fill the increased demand for functional containers. Willows are strong and flexible and the natural kink in each stem gives tightness and resilience to the finished basket. The generous sizes and assortment in shapes of our Willow Baskets enable them to be mainstay storage solutions in the home and garden with a quality that will allow them to become heirloom pieces for generations to come. column4: Woven by hand using select quality materials and traditional methods, the complex weave of each Willow Basket tells the story of the time and meticulous effort spent to craft each piece. Weaving is a centuries-old trade that was driven during the Industrial Revolution to fill the increased demand for functional containers. Willows are strong and flexible and the natural kink in each stem gives tightness and resilience to the finished basket. The generous sizes and assortment in shapes of our Willow Baskets enable them to be mainstay storage solutions in the home and garden with a quality that will allow them to become heirloom pieces for generations to come. Bring indoors during rain and frost to preserve longevity.

Certainly perfect for indicating address information, these signs can also combine to point the way, make a statement, display preferences, provoke a smile, or, in the case of the compass, to provide directional bearings. For walls, doors, fences, gardens, patios, family rooms, entryways, and anywhere else the imaginative decorator can conceive, HomArtâ€™s Cast Iron Signs vary in width but are all 3 inches high to ensure complete compatibility. From the numerals 0 through 9 to words (dogs, cats, beach, welcome, in, eat) to abbreviations (WC for water closet and No. for number) to symbols (arrows, thumbs up, ampersands), home decorators will delight in combining these ingenious communicators to suit their particular purposes, humors, and informational needs. Certainly perfect for indicating address information, these signs can also combine to point the way, make a statement, display preferences, provoke a smile, or, in the case of the compass, to provide directional bearings. For walls, doors, fences, gardens, patios, family rooms, entryways, and anywhere else the imaginative decorator can conceive, HomArtâ€™s Cast Iron Signs vary in width but are all 3 inches high to ensure complete compatibility. column4: Woven by hand using select quality materials and traditional methods, the complex weave of each Willow Basket tells the story of the time and meticulous effort spent to craft each piece. Weaving is a centuries-old trade that was driven during the Industrial Revolution to fill the increased demand for functional containers. Willows are strong and flexible and the natural kink in each stem gives tightness and resilience to the finished basket. The generous sizes and assortment in shapes of our Willow Baskets enable them to be mainstay storage solutions in the home and garden with a quality that will allow them to become heirloom pieces for generations to come. Bring indoors during rain and frost to preserve longevity.

Woven by hand using select quality materials and traditional methods, the complex weave of each Willow Basket tells the story of the time and meticulous effort spent to craft each piece. Weaving is a centuries-old trade that was driven during the Industrial Revolution to fill the increased demand for functional containers. Willows are strong and flexible and the natural kink in each stem gives tightness and resilience to the finished basket. The generous sizes and assortment in shapes of our Willow Baskets enable them to be mainstay storage solutions in the home and garden with a quality that will allow them to become heirloom pieces for generations to come. Bring indoors during rain and frost to preserve longevity.

column4: Reproductions of terra cotta canteens become objects of art when elevated on a metal stand. The stand is removable allowing the pot to be rotated, hung, or displayed in multitudes of ways.

Corral mail, magazines, keys, and coats in style with this good-looking and totally functional wall mounted organizer. Made of wood with a subtle whitewash finish and a plethora of metal hooks. Hangs with 2 keyhole hangers.
Varying sizes of Kiri Wood beads are strung together in this oversized decorative strand to add a fun pop of interest to a door knob, a chair rail or hung on the wall with a forged iron nail.
